  "time_ut": 1656168610,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd\u00a0 \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bcd !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Police headquarters appeals to the public!",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Police Headquarters has instructed all police officers not to ask the police to open the tanks where the public has stored fuel and to keep the police officers away from opening the tanks.",
        "This was stated in a special statement issued by the police media unit.",
        "It has been reported that people in line to the police are requesting to open the tanks that have been stored in the fuel storage.",
        "In this case do not ask the police officers working at the public petrol stations to open the tanks where the fuel is stored.",
        "It also created a tense situation at the petrol station due to the activities of a few underworld gangs who tried to open the fuel tanks with the intervention of the police. This will cause the police to be held accountable.",
        "A statement from the police media unit said that it was not the responsibility of the police to open and inspect the fuel tanks and that only those with permission should do so safely."
      ],
